snippet.title: Sleeping Dogs Ghost Pig DLC Gameplay
snippet.description: Become the elusive movie star with the Ghost Pig mask. Dogeyes' black fedora hat, an assassin's straw hat, and a lone sheriff's hat are also included in this free pack.
